.DT
set_open_func
Disk World creator help
set_open_func

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_open_func -  This method sets the function to evaluate to check to see if the shop is open or not.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_open_func(function func)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^func%^RESET%^ - the open function
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/print_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the function to evaluate to check to see if the shop
is open or not.  This should set any error messages which are needed.
The objects are passed in as an argument in the do_print functions
and nothing is passed in for the collection check.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_open_func(), do_print(), do_print_copies(), do_collect()

.EP

